<h4 id="talk-is-cheap-show-me-the-math"><strong>Talk is cheap! Show me the math?</strong></h4>
<p>This blog collects, refines, and presents math concepts behind machine learning in a minimalistic way.</p>

<h4 id="some-content-in-chinese"><strong>Some content in Chinese?</strong></h4>
<p>For most topics, I can write faster in my native language. 
I believe that the perfect translation technique is coming soon
and language barrier will no longer exist in the internet.</p>

